info.author: Joerg Raedler
info.description:
FuGrep means fuzzy grep, which is inexact string
        matching.  FuGrep is a replacement for agrepy, which works nice but
        has a very unpythonic interface. FuGrep uses agrep for the underlying
        functions and uses concepts of agrepy, but replaces the python wrapper
        with its own code.
info.name: FuGrep
info.summary: Python bindings to agrep, a fuzzy string matching tool
